---
import Base from "../layouts/BaseLayout.astro";
import Header from "../components/Header.astro";
import Footer from "../components/Footer.astro";
---
<Base title="About"><Fragment slot="header"><Header /></Fragment>

  <section class="relative pt-28 pb-16 overflow-hidden bg-subtle-grid" style="background:linear-gradient(135deg,#fafaf9 0%,#ffffff 30%,#ede9fe 100%)">
    <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto px-6 lg:px-8 relative">
      <div class="max-w-2xl"><p class="sl">About</p><h1 class="text-4xl sm:text-5xl font-heading font-bold text-stone-900 leading-tight mb-5">Infrastructure for the genome</h1><p class="text-lg text-stone-600 max-w-xl">Protomon Labs builds the platforms, standards, and tools that make genomic research possible at scale.</p></div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="py-20">
    <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto px-6 lg:px-8">
      <div class="grid md:grid-cols-3 gap-12 items-start">
        <div class="md:col-span-1"><div class="aspect-[3/4] rounded-xl bg-stone-50 flex items-center justify-center border border-stone-100"><img src="/logo.svg" alt="" class="w-28 h-28 opacity-20" /></div></div>
        <div class="md:col-span-2 space-y-5 text-stone-600 leading-relaxed">
          <p>Genomic research produces extraordinary tools. But scaling and maintaining them over years requires dedicated engineering investment that the current funding model doesn't fully sustain. Protomon Labs builds that sustaining layer — open-source genomic infrastructure that's maintained, documented, and production-ready. We complement the work of academic groups by providing the engineering layer that temporary project funding can't cover.</p>
          <p>Everything we build is AGPL-licensed, keeping the work in the commons, with a dual-license path for organisations that need closed use. Our revenue comes from support contracts and custom development — not from gating features.</p>
          <p>We're based in Cambridge, UK, and we partner with sequencing centers, biobanks, and tool developers working at genomic scale.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="py-20 bg-stone-50 border-y border-stone-100 reveal">
    <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto px-6 lg:px-8">
      <div class="max-w-xl mb-10"><p class="sl">Approach</p><h2 class="text-3xl font-heading font-bold text-stone-900">Our approach</h2></div>
      <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-5">
        <div class="card">
          <div class="icon-ring"><svg class="w-5 h-5" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><polyline points="16 18 22 12 16 6"/><polyline points="8 6 2 12 8 18"/></svg></div>
          <h3 class="font-heading font-semibold text-stone-900 mb-2">Engineering-first</h3>
          <p class="text-sm text-stone-600 leading-relaxed">We apply professional software engineering practices — versioning, testing, documentation, CI/CD — to infrastructure that researchers and facilities can depend on.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="card">
          <div class="icon-ring"><svg class="w-5 h-5" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M12 22s8-4 8-10V5l-8-3-8 3v7c0 6 8 10 8 10z"/></svg></div>
          <h3 class="font-heading font-semibold text-stone-900 mb-2">Sustainable funding</h3>
          <p class="text-sm text-stone-600 leading-relaxed">Support contracts and custom development fund ongoing maintenance. The code remains open; the value is in having a team accountable for it.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="card">
          <div class="icon-ring"><svg class="w-5 h-5" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><rect x="3" y="11" width="18" height="10" rx="2"/><circle cx="12" cy="5" r="2"/><path d="M12 7v4"/></svg></div>
          <h3 class="font-heading font-semibold text-stone-900 mb-2">Open with protection</h3>
          <p class="text-sm text-stone-600 leading-relaxed">AGPL licensing ensures community contributions stay in the commons, with a dual-license path for commercial integration.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="card">
          <div class="icon-ring"><svg class="w-5 h-5" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M12 2L2 7l10 5 10-5-10-5z"/><path d="M2 17l10 5 10-5"/><path d="M2 12l10 5 10-5"/></svg></div>
          <h3 class="font-heading font-semibold text-stone-900 mb-2">Standards to life</h3>
          <p class="text-sm text-stone-600 leading-relaxed">Reference implementations, SDKs, and certification tooling that make interoperability standards practical and deployable.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="py-20">
    <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto px-6 lg:px-8">
      <div class="max-w-xl mb-10"><p class="sl">Markets</p><h2 class="text-3xl font-heading font-bold text-stone-900">Who we work with</h2></div>
      <div class="grid md:grid-cols-3 gap-5">
        <div class="card">
          <div class="icon-ring"><svg class="w-5 h-5" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><rect x="2" y="3" width="20" height="14" rx="2"/><path d="M8 21h8"/><path d="M12 17v4"/></svg></div>
          <h3 class="font-heading font-semibold text-stone-900 mb-2">Sequencing centers &amp; biobanks</h3>
          <p class="text-sm text-stone-600 leading-relaxed">Facilities processing genomic data at scale that need reliable, maintained software infrastructure.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="card">
          <div class="icon-ring"><svg class="w-5 h-5" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><circle cx="18" cy="5" r="3"/><circle cx="6" cy="12" r="3"/><circle cx="18" cy="19" r="3"/><line x1="8.59" y1="13.51" x2="15.42" y2="17.49"/><line x1="15.41" y1="6.51" x2="8.59" y2="10.49"/></svg></div>
          <h3 class="font-heading font-semibold text-stone-900 mb-2">Tool developers</h3>
          <p class="text-sm text-stone-600 leading-relaxed">Teams building new genomic methods who want to focus on science while we handle infrastructure and maintenance.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="card">
          <div class="icon-ring"><svg class="w-5 h-5" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M17 21v-2a4 4 0 0 0-4-4H5a4 4 0 0 0-4 4v2"/><circle cx="9" cy="7" r="4"/><path d="M23 21v-2a4 4 0 0 0-3-3.87"/><path d="M16 3.13a4 4 0 0 1 0 7.75"/></svg></div>
          <h3 class="font-heading font-semibold text-stone-900 mb-2">Standards organisations</h3>
          <p class="text-sm text-stone-600 leading-relaxed">Groups developing community standards who need maintained reference implementations and conformance tooling.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="relative py-20 overflow-hidden" style="background:linear-gradient(135deg,#5b21b6,#4c1d95,#3b0764)">
    <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-subtle-grid opacity-[0.08]" />
    <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto px-6 lg:px-8 text-center relative">
      <div class="max-w-xl mx-auto">
        <h2 class="text-3xl font-heading font-bold text-white mb-3">Building the foundations of genomic discovery</h2>
        <p class="text-cobalt-200 leading-relaxed mb-8">We partner with sequencing centers, biobanks, and tool developers working at genomic scale.</p>
        <a href="/contact" class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 px-8 py-3 bg-white hover:bg-stone-50 text-stone-800 font-medium rounded-xl transition-all active:scale-[0.97]">Get in touch →</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

<Fragment slot="footer"><Footer /></Fragment></Base>